  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "It's not about how you feel, but what you provide inside that hole I've been up, later and later thinking about my role Not a biological, but still loving hole I know you never saw me as a start But something that tore your whole world apart Hear you say it's not what you feel divided With all of the fancy things that shine I feel good about the love I provided Respect and kindness given to you from the start True wealth kid, comes from your fucking heart I can't hide myself I don't expect you to understand I just hope I can explain What it's like to be a man",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 6.239999771118164,
      "text": "It's not about how you feel, but what you provide inside that hole",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 11.039999961853027,
      "text": "I've been up, later and later thinking about my role",
      "start": 6.579999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 14.199999809265137,
      "text": "Not a biological, but still loving hole",
      "start": 11.039999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 16.979999542236328,
      "text": "I know you never saw me as a start",
      "start": 14.199999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 21.239999771118164,
      "text": "But something that tore your whole world apart",
      "start": 16.979999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 24.219999313354492,
      "text": "Hear you say it's not what you feel divided",
      "start": 21.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 26.719999313354492,
      "text": "With all of the fancy things that shine",
      "start": 24.219999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 29.040000915527344,
      "text": "I feel good about the love I provided",
      "start": 26.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 32.540000915527344,
      "text": "Respect and kindness given to you from the start",
      "start": 29.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 36.18000030517578,
      "text": "True wealth kid, comes from your fucking heart",
      "start": 32.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 37.619998931884766,
      "text": "I can't hide myself",
      "start": 36.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 42.2400016784668,
      "text": "I don't expect you to understand",
      "start": 39.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 45.97999954223633,
      "text": "I just hope I can explain",
      "start": 42.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 49.439998626708984,
      "text": "What it's like to be a man",
      "start": 46.29999923706055
    }
  ],
  "unlock": {
    "card": "card-30",
    "fragments": 10
  }
}